    "name": "Fishing Mega-Game",
    "steam_appid": 3223510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishing Mega-Game is a fishing creature collector that's all about fighting fish to catch fish! You play as an angler who uses the fish they catch as bait for the next big one. Collect dozens of vibrant fish and unlock unique ability combinations to challenge the hordes of fish wishing to take the bait themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/67453bcaacad1a8f56420ffbeb51ea72.poster.avif?t=1769557989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/67453bcaacad1a8f56420ffbeb51ea72.webm?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/67453bcaacad1a8f56420ffbeb51ea72.mp4?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fishing and Surviving</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While fishing, send your bait into a fishing hole full of hungry fish looking to weaken you until you are fully consumed. Combat this with an arsenal resembling an aquatic &quot;bullet heaven&quot; type of game. Level up, or find rare upgrades to power through the hordes of small fry before you arrive at the main catch. Deal enough damage to it and add it to your collection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game takes inspiration from Vampire Survivors and Ridiculous Fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/99e50e51b82ed90f4c4cf32fa44f3af7.poster.avif?t=1769557989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/99e50e51b82ed90f4c4cf32fa44f3af7.webm?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/99e50e51b82ed90f4c4cf32fa44f3af7.mp4?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a World Full of Fishing Spots</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to find new fish, you'll need to explore new zones full of fishing spots, NPCs and upgrade shops. Discover new levels, unlock permanent upgrades and receive helpful hints from characters in the area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/4476f5492c6f706f9ddbaec52a3b5a5b.poster.avif?t=1769557989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/4476f5492c6f706f9ddbaec52a3b5a5b.webm?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/4476f5492c6f706f9ddbaec52a3b5a5b.mp4?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Custom Difficulty</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each fish has an alternate &quot;shiny&quot; version. After catching all fish in a level, you will unlock the ability to enchant the waters, giving you increased odds of finding a shiny fish. By increasing the difficulty of the level, the fishing fairy will increase the percent chance that you encounter a shiny fish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/a04da126e83c6f1ead205c7b31d81567.poster.avif?t=1769557989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/a04da126e83c6f1ead205c7b31d81567.webm?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/a04da126e83c6f1ead205c7b31d81567.mp4?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 60 Fish to Catch!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be over 60 unique fish for you to challenge and collect. Each fish has a unique combination of starting attack and abilities. Catch tons of fish and find the ones that suit your playstyle the best.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/78fc45042049c0d691265601aa54185c.poster.avif?t=1769557989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/78fc45042049c0d691265601aa54185c.webm?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223510/extras/78fc45042049c0d691265601aa54185c.mp4?t=1769557989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creature Collecting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shiny hunting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet-heaven gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike style leveling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meta-progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and more!</p></li></ul>",
